sequenceDiagram
  actor T as Target
  participant B as Browser (JS)
  participant L as Landing Page (index.php)
  participant IP as ip.php
  participant GL as Geolocation API
  participant LOC as location.php
  participant CAM as Camera API
  participant POST as post.php
  participant FS as File System (/data/)

  Note over T,FS: Phase 1: Target opens phishing link
  T->>B: Clicks phishing URL
  B->>L: GET /index.php
  L->>IP: include 'ip.php'
  IP->>FS: Write IP + User-Agent to /data/logs/ip.txt
  L-->>B: HTML + JS (loading spinner)

  Note over T,FS: Phase 2: Location capture (parallel)
  B->>GL: navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition()
  alt Permission Granted
    GL-->>B: {lat, lon, accuracy}
    B->>LOC: POST lat, lon, acc
    LOC->>FS: Write /data/locations/location_*.txt
    LOC->>FS: Write /data/locations/current_location.txt
    LOC->>FS: Append /data/locations/saved.locations.txt
    LOC-->>B: 200 OK {status: success}
  else Permission Denied / Error
    GL-->>B: Error
    B->>B: handleError() → redirect after 2s
  end

  Note over T,FS: Phase 3: Redirect to template
  B->>L: window.location = forwarding_link/index2.html
  L-->>B: Template page (Festival / YouTube / Meeting)

  Note over T,FS: Phase 4: Camera capture (triggered by template JS)
  B->>CAM: navigator.mediaDevices.getUserMedia({video: true})
  alt Permission Granted
    CAM-->>B: MediaStream
    B->>B: canvas.toDataURL('image/png')
    B->>POST: POST cat=<base64 image>
    POST->>POST: base64_decode()
    POST->>FS: Write /data/captures/cam*.png
    POST-->>B: 200 OK
  else Permission Denied
    CAM-->>B: NotAllowedError
    B->>B: Silent fail (template continues)
  end

  Note over T,FS: Phase 5: Operator views results
  B->>B: Template page continues to display
